<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Đổi mật khẩu</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/views/resources/css/change-pass.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.0/jquery.min.js"> </script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.1/css/all.css"
        integrity="sha384-50oBUHEmvpQ+1lW4y57PTFmhCaXp0ML5d60M1M7uH2+nqUivzIebhndOJK28anvf" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>

<body id="body">
    <div class="template">
        <header class="header-style">
            <label class="label-click" id="label-click"><i class="fas fa-list-ul"></i></label>
            <div class="Logo">
                <a href=""><img class="Logo-img" src="/views/resources/image/Logo.png" alt="Logo"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="function-name">
                <a href="/homepage" id="posName">Phòng đào tạo</a>
            </div>
            <div class="regularly-action" id="regularly-action">
                <a href="/logout"> <span><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt" style="margin-right: 5px"></i></span> Đăng
                    xuất</a>
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="Left" id="Left">
            <div class="home-page">
                <a href="/homepage"> <span><i class="fas fa-home"></i></span> <span id="span1"> Trang chủ </span></a>
            </div>

            <div class="Function">
                <p class="func-click" id="func-click"> <span><i class="fas fa-radiation-alt"></i></span> <span
                        id="span2">Công việc</span> </p>
                <div id="showFunction" style="display: none">
                    <div class="function-student" id="function-student" style="display: none">
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="/student/editStudentInfo">Thông tin cá nhân</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/student/coursesinfo">Trang của tôi</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/student/grades">Kết quả học tập</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/student/resis-course">Đăng ký môn học</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="function-teacher" id="function-teacher" style="display: none">
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="/teacher/editTeacherInfo">Thông tin cá nhân</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/teacher/coursesinfo">Trang của tôi</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="function-admin" id="function-admin" style="display: none">
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="/management/add">Thêm tài khoản</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/management/del">Xoá tài khoản</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/management/find">Tìm kiếm tài khoản</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/management/renew">Cấp lại mật khẩu</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/admin/createSubject">Tạo môn học</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/admin/deleteSubject">Xoá môn học</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/admin/stopRegSubject">Dừng đăng kí môn học</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/admin/regsubafter">Đăng kí môn học trễ</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="Cpass">
                <p class="pCPass" id="Cpass"><span><i class="fas fa-key"></i></span><span id="span3">Đổi mật
                        khẩu</span></p>
            </div>
            <div class="About">
                <p class="pAbout" id="pAbout"> <span><i class="fas fa-question"></i></span> <span id="span4">Thông tin
                        thêm</span> </p>
                <div id="aboutShow" style="display: none">
                    <ul id="student-about" style="display: none">
                        <li>Sinh viên đăng ký môn học khi đợt mở môn học bắt đầu</li>
                        <li>Sinh viên xem kết quả học tập hiện tại</li>
                        <li>Sinh viên thay đổi thông tin cá nhân khi cần thiết</li>
                        <li>Sinh viên sử dụng trang của tôi để coi thông tin các môn học</li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul id="teacher-about" style="display:none">
                        <li>Giảng viên có thể vô trang của tôi để đưa các thông tin yêu cầu cho lớp mình đang
                            dạy</li>
                        <li>Giảng viên có thể thay đổi thông tin cá nhân khi cần thiết</li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul id="admin-about" style="display:none">
                        <li>Phòng đào tạo thao tác với các tài khoản của hệ thống</li>
                        <li>Phòng đào tạo chỉnh sửa danh sách lớp học</li>
                        <li>Phòng đào tạo cấp lại mậu khẩu cho tài khoản</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <div class="disable" id="disable"></div>
            <div class="work-area">
                <fieldset>
                    <div class="divTitle">
                        <p>Thay đổi mật khẩu</p>
                    </div>
                    <form action="/change-pass/done" method="POST">
                        <p id="AlertShow1">Mật khẩu cũ không trùng khớp</p>
                        <div class="smPass">
                            <p class="passText"><span id="old_icn"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i></span><input
                                    style="border:none" type="password" name="oPass" id="oldPass"
                                    placeholder="Mật khẩu hiện tại" maxlength="30" tabindex="2"></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="clearfix"></div>
                        <p id="AlertShow2">Mật khẩu mới phải lớn hơn 7 ký tự</p>
                        <div class="nPass">
                            <p class="newPass"> <span id="new_icn"><i class="far fa-eye"></i></span><input
                                    style="border:none" type="password" name="nPass" id="newPass"
                                    placeholder="Mật khẩu mới" maxlength="30" tabindex="2">
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <p id="AlertShow3">Mật khẩu nhập lại không trùng khớp</p>
                        <div class="rePass">
                            <p class="rPass"><span id="re_icn"><i class="fas fa-key"></i></span> <input type="password"
                                    placeholder="Nhập lại mật khẩu mới" style="border:none" name="rPass"
                                    id="rePass"></p>
                        </div>
                        <input type="Submit" value="Thay đổi" class="btnSubmit" id="btnSubmit">
                    </form>
                </fieldset>
        </nav>
    </div>
    <script src="/views/resources/js/all_change-pass.js"></script>
</body>

</html>